      "span_text": "In particular, in the seminal work of Seiberg and Witten [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] it was shown that the low-energy dynamics of N = 2 supersymmetric gauge theories is encoded in the properties of an associated hyperelliptic Seiberg-Witten (SW) curve."
